data.description: Pride of homeownership shines through in McCormick Meadows! This open-concept home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with fresh new paint inside and out! Enjoy cooking in this kitchen w/ granite countertops, an expansive island with eating space, stainless steel appliances, natural gas range, and solid granite countertops. All bedrooms are located upstairs including the primary suite that offers a HUGE walk-in closet and 5 pc bathroom. Don't miss the covered patio, wonderful fully fenced backyard that's great for entertaining and gardening with privacy offered by the green belt. Rare 3 car garage for storage and toys! Minutes from town center and Hwy16! Don't miss this opportunity!
